////Muscles - Location

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 - Soft tissue of Shoulder MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Muscles' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Deltoid muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Pectoralis major muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Coracobrachial muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Teres major muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Infraspinatus muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Supraspinatus muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Subscapularis muscle' radio button is enabled
And 'Teres minor muscle' radio button is enabled

And 'Pathology' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Deltoid muscle' radio button
Then 'Pars clavicularis' radio button is enabled
And 'Acromial pars' radio button is enabled
And 'Pars spinalis' radio button is enabled
